    <date day="19" month="October" year="2009"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes an XML-based protocol for mapping service
identifiers and geodetic or civic location information to service
contact URIs.  In particular, it can be used to determine the
location-appropriate Public Safety Answering Point (PSAP) for
emergency services.

This document is a revision of the original LoST specification,
descrbed in RFC 5222.
	 </t>
